ore": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863859522,45974302,3503]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60220546]知者默[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:20):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，今天要是一天就4020了该怎么搞[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>为什么要一直问 我早上不是说什么情况才会出问题么 <br/>一直问怎么办的麻烦往前面看", "lou": 1881, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 863859522, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775625901}, {"pid": 863860207, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:27", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "散户现在都还没进很多  都是犹犹豫豫的 <br/>目前拉升主要是量化跟进。机构量化柚子都在进  只有散户犹犹豫豫", "lou": 1882, "content_length": 92, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775626042}, {"pid": 863860891, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:33", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863860489,45974302,3505]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=23841879]dsjohn5302[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:29):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，如何看待赵姨的走势，涨幅快要超过德子了[s:a2:中枪](应该说德子跳水很奇怪吧)[/quote]<br/>如果不是因为减持  现在就是原厂的节奏  模组换原厂 是一个正在进行的趋势", "lou": 1883, "content_length": 69, "reply_to": 863860489, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775626405}, {"pid": 863861298, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:36", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863860586,45974302,3506]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:30):[/b]<br/><br/>拉成这样居然还没散户进场[s:a2:自戳双目]我都满仓躺了[/quote]<br/>你不要看这个楼  你出去看看  谁TM敢明知道今天会高开还盘前叫人激进的。你看到了@我一下", "lou": 1884, "content_length": 84, "reply_to": 863860586, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775626608}, {"pid": 863861407, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:37", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863860908,45974302,3506]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=1241533]嘻哈小树苗[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:33):[/b]<br/><br/>散户为什么不进啊，我现在8.5成仓了[/quote]<br/>散户就是想卖  你信不信 他也不是卖 他是10块卖  10块5买回来  11块卖  11块5又买回来<br/>你不信你问多两个人", "lou": 1885, "content_length": 93, "reply_to": 863860908, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775626667}, {"pid": 863861710, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863861523,45974302,3508]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63288314]雪山阿福[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:38):[/b]<br/><br/>没有量化打板了吗。这么好涨停也才100家[/quote]<br/>量化调整策略了 被弱化了 现在是跟大资金后面 没有办法冲前面了", "lou": 1886, "content_length": 61, "reply_to": 863861523, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775626819}, {"pid": 863863134, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 128, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "我知道你们的  平时涨0.5%都要T两次  如果今天你们还是这样  至少80%的人卖飞<br/>所以我今天就告诉你们 具体什么情况才可能是顶  今天出现了吗？那有什么好卖的 <br/>我今天心情很好  不想骂人 不要硬凑上来", "lou": 1887, "content_length": 170, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775627587}, {"pid": 863863361, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 13:55", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863863104,45974302,3511]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67156308]xenoblade4[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:52):[/b]<br/><br/>赵姨早上主力跑了十多个亿，散户玩命接，快到中午主力发现买盘没完了又回头买[s:ac:哭笑]不过全天主力还是大幅净卖的，涨幅板块里垫底，得考验明天大韩双C不带飞了今天散户获利盘卖出的支撑[/quote]<br/>行情好而已  减持状态的股在分化的时候还要被考验的", "lou": 1888, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 863863104, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775627704}, {"pid": 863864167, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 30, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:02", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863863794,45974302,3512]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60206245]xtt1211[/uid] (2026-04-08 13:58):[/b]<br/><br/>逻辑不对吧，这个点位散户真的会接么[s:ac:擦汗]<br/>创始人减持是实打实的收割小散户，狼大说的要不是今天大盘行情消化，按个跌停是没问题的<br/>主力出货也不太对劲，减持是到4.30后的，现在出货他砸他自己么，尤其现在赵姨在还低位<br/>看量我现在只是怀疑会不会借这个消息洗筹码，或者说有没有机构进来了，但是这又不像是赵姨的一贯操作[s:ac:愁]<br/>盘后看树哥或者其他大佬有没有复盘分析吧[/quote]<br/>散户或者散大户买了很多 大部分这种散户在找低位个股的时候甚至不看一眼F10 别我为什么知道", "lou": 1889, "content_length": 88, "reply_to": 863863794, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775628124}, {"pid": 863864606, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 20, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:05", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863864253,45974302,3513]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989744]两极反转我要成功[/uid] (2026-04-08 14:02):[/b]<br/><br/>有一点想不明白，今天这么好的行情 全是因为盘前金毛taco了吗？如果是的话，这次市场反响咋这么强烈[/quote]<br/>一个诱因 <br/>今天不TACO也要杀跌后低位拉起来的。", "lou": 1890, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 863864253, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775628349}, {"pid": 863865865, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:16", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863865326,45974302,3515]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65768926]好好看好好学不好[/uid] (2026-04-08 14:11):[/b]<br/><br/>，，，卖飞+1，反应太迟钝了，没有理解到狼大说的是啥意思[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>这还用做阅读理解？我今天说得有一点点歧义？", "lou": 1891, "content_length": 47, "reply_to": 863865326, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775628987}, {"pid": 863866310, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863866073,45974302,3516]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66989363]鱼饵啊啊[/uid] (2026-04-08 14:18):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大今天开盘没跟大盘涨的，应该是昨天大涨今天歇了吧？[s:ac:哭笑]你知道我说的哪几个。。。[/quote]<br/>除了减持  剩下的就是前面抱团的 ，这些是借今天大盘普涨 做一些减持，并不表示这些抱团的行情就结束了。这些今天弱是因为前两天强", "lou": 1892, "content_length": 123, "reply_to": 863866073, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775629199}, {"pid": 863867415, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863867091,45974302,3517]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64092780]AKM无糖[/uid] (2026-04-08 14:26):[/b]<br/><br/>没太理解狼大说的1000e是啥意思，缩量1000e吗[/quote]<br/>。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。", "lou": 1893, "content_length": 37, "reply_to": 863867091, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775629759}, {"pid": 863867621, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 67, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们问得这么蠢  我甚至不知道怎么说明天应该看什么迹象要做减仓<br/>完全不理解你们是否看懂", "lou": 1894, "content_length": 80, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775629847}, {"pid": 863869829, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 42, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "散户开始进来了  终于看见了", "lou": 1895, "content_length": 24, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775630860}, {"pid": 863870562, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 8, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863870161,45974302,3523]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65490615]子午卯酉甲乙丙丁[/uid] (2026-04-08 14:50):[/b]<br/><br/>散户应该不敢追高吧，喜欢买那种+2+3的[/quote]<br/>应该属于打沙枪那种 就是什么都买一点 低位的买多一点。 喜欢买没涨的肯定多一点。", "lou": 1896, "content_length": 79, "reply_to": 863870161, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775631181}, {"pid": 863871167, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 56, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 14:57", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "OK  这个时候3993.99 这个不是高点 放心了 机构控盘合格", "lou": 1897, "content_length": 47, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775631464}, {"pid": 863871849, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 49, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 15:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "嗯 目前还在机构控盘中 符合预判，这里GJD队没主动进场。我说的。", "lou": 1898, "content_length": 59, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775631784}, {"pid": 863872747, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 81, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-08 15:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "简单总结 这里并没有超出预判，也就是目前还在做局的范围内，之前被金融砸了两天导致机构成本有所抬高，目前哪怕4020位置卖他们也不会挣太多 算是勉强少亏点吧，所以整体思路没有反转，仍然是机构自救和吸引资金进场的过程，需要看散户是不是能在这两天重拾信心进场，然后机构会在谈判前把筹码好好的交给这些散户，如果进场资金足够到反转那是另外一件事，属于突发事件<br/><br/>你问我散户为什么会这么蠢去接呢<br/>因为指数涨起来了，散户会选择性遗忘一切不利因素冲动下单", "lou": 1899, "content_length": 424, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775632177}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155489, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109303, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "异乡猫", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109315, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,67082978,66949654,65530601,60630412,60240136,66038632,63481990,61973100,60192597,66985104,19043499,39108806,41714633,7046671,65647302,40696141,3481707,654677,39235785,66063392,39314790,67071606,66251279,42126891,61602239,4785041,42995612,67024871,62241578,64199867,11586486,5641907,66685489,66633842,65208818,42941765,,42964685,42181525,14317962,67086252,34699482,62593385,67000864,64005788,62799978,60424140,42468630,61